abstract="The Internet of Things is transforming the way we interact with our houses and cities. The advance of technology granted a wide range of possibilities to connect virtually any device and collect data on its use; however, it seems that we are not considering the human that will interact with it. In this paper, I will present how a Human-Centered Design approach was adopted in the development of a Smart Building office.",
