abstract="Acceleration of the aging process of population urges the research and innovative design of geriatric rehabilitation products. This paper introduces natural interaction technology to geriatric rehabilitation products through analysis of the elderly's physiological and psychological characteristics. This paper aims at exploring new approaches to geriatric rehabilitation products design, approaches that are innovative in both of the two aspects: product function and interactive experiences of using the product.",
