abstract="Based on the analysis of traditional emergency drills and simulated emergency drill characteristics, the construction and express method of structured scene model was proposed, including the emergency scene classification, the setting of evolution and development conditions and the structured expression of emergency scene. The scene-driven key technology and model was described, such as the evolutionary relationship of scenes, the reasoning model of scene chain and transition model of scene. On the basis, the emergency drill model of scene-driven was proposed. The model is dynamic and has high similarity with the real emergencies, which plays an important role to improve the effect of emergency drills.",
